<body>
<h1> Syntax </h1>
<br>
mount [animal]<br>
dismount [animal]<br>
<br>
<h1> Description </h1>
<br>
The mount and dismount commands are used by riders to get on/off their<br>
animals.  Some mounts may wear items, such as barding, and some pets may<br>
wear things like saddlebags.  The syntax is put saddlebags on [mount].<br>
</html>
</body>
